# =====================  ARTICLES  =========================
############################################################

### ARTICLES – Empty filters
POST http://localhost:3001/api/articles/search
Content-Type: application/json

{}


### ARTICLES – Subject filter  (mapped to Subjects table)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/articles/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subjects": ["Machine Learning"]
}

### ARTICLES – Subject filter + sort by citations
POST http://localhost:3001/api/articles/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subjects": ["Machine Learning"],
  "fromYear": 2018,
  "toYear": 2024,
  "sortBy": "citations"
}



### ARTICLES – Author filter
POST http://localhost:3001/api/articles/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "author": "John"
}



### ARTICLES – Year range
POST http://localhost:3001/api/articles/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromYear": 2019,
  "toYear": 2022
}


### ARTICLES – Keyword + Limit + Offset
POST http://localhost:3001/api/articles/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "keyword": "chemistry",
  "limit": 5,
  "offset": 0
}


### ARTICLES – Complex Filters
POST http://localhost:3001/api/articles/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subject": "biology",
  "fromYear": 2015,
  "toYear": 2024,
  "author": "Li",
  "keyword": "cell",
  "limit": 20,
  "offset": 0
}




